- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper utilizes machine learning techniques for anomaly detection. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with the ADS-B system and its management. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also a possible category as the ADS-B system is a type of wireless communication network.
